snippet.title: Sexy Talented & Original Music Party (STOMP) - Amber Havana
snippet.description:
Amber Havana and Soul-La Productions hosted STOMP (Sexy Talented and Original Music Party) at Mt. Tabor Theater in SE Portland. January 7th 2012 was the first time Soul-La hosted such an event and they plan on having this event every month. STOMP consists of music from popular Portland bands, Portland fashion designers, DJs and more. Keep up with The Portland Pick, because we will be following Amber on her Portland adventures.

Check out http://www.soullaproductions.com/

As always, follow us at facebook.com/theportlandpick and on Twitter - @theportlandpick
